{"tid":829958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師：鋸走殘枝或犯盜竊","createTime":"2018-09-21T00:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T05:02:13.000Z","uid":36494,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"31e2e68911382a3649783fcc831ab96e7ad34ea9","tid":829958,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180921&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20504574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180921%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20504574&d=05Nod63SsUJ3W1ecdT50tDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=b304b5e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180921%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20504574&h=f37c4882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180921&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20504574</a><br />\n<br />\n大律師：鋸走殘枝或犯盜竊<br />\n<br />\n本報訊】山竹過後，處處冧樹！近日不少巿民向路邊已塌下的樟樹埋手，鋸走樹幹欲帶回家自用，以為無傷大雅，但大律師陸偉雄警告鋸樹者有可能已觸犯《盜竊罪條例》，最高可判監十年，理由是若大樹種植政府土地，即使它已塌下仍然是政府財物，故鋸走樹的一部份形同盜竊。除非政府人員事前已把樹丟棄到垃圾站，即是明顯放棄擁有權，那麼鋸樹者行為才可能視為合法的「拾垃圾（拾荒）」。<br />\n陸偉雄解釋，塌下的樹絕不等於無價值，例如政府有可能把樹木再造成其他有價值的東西，故確是財物。此外，若在政府土地上非法砍伐或摧毀樹木或生長中的植物，亦會觸犯《林區及郊區條例》，一經定罪最高可判監一年及罰款2.5萬。"},{"pid":"da49048cf92e50dccc83cbbb9916698c51133cf2","tid":829958,"uid":122601,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"政府財物 阻塞通道點計咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7b7d65337a94829c08a912ce4b52eab7edf5bf","tid":829958,"uid":155343,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:23:31.000Z","msg":"得個講字 點會真係去拉哂班廢老"},{"pid":"ad889f1c279f92713b78c7f6ae638b6a5a9b150e","tid":829958,"uid":205530,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10a693c055e51ad1e5720783fb8ae91ff13e4eaa","tid":829958,"uid":52403,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1